      "abbreviation": "PX160802",
      "description": "This screening protocol includes nine proxy-administered questions from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) Screening Questionnaire for Child and Teen Immunization. Parents or guardians are asked to respond to yes-or-no questions.",
